stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: Container starts (model NOT loaded)

    state Idle {
        [*] --> waiting
        waiting: Waiting for first request
        note right of waiting: VRAM = 0 GB
    }

    Idle --> Loading: Request arrives

    state Loading {
        [*] --> download_check
        download_check: Check model cached?
        download_check --> load_weights: cached
        download_check --> download_model: not cached
        download_model --> load_weights
        load_weights: Load to GPU
        load_weights --> warmup
        warmup: Warm-up inference
        note right of load_weights: ASR: ~3.4 GB<br/>TTS: ~2-3 GB<br/>Cold start: 5-8s
    }

    Loading --> Active: Model ready

    state Active {
        [*] --> ready
        ready: Ready for inference
        ready --> processing: Request
        processing: GPU inference
        processing --> ready: Response
        note right of ready: VRAM allocated<br/>Idle timer running
    }

    Active --> Active: New request (reset timer)
    Active --> Unloading: Idle timeout (300s)

    state Unloading {
        [*] --> delete_model
        delete_model: del model
        delete_model --> empty_cache
        empty_cache: torch.cuda.empty_cache()
        empty_cache --> gc_collect
        gc_collect: gc.collect()
        note right of empty_cache: VRAM freed
    }

    Unloading --> Idle: VRAM released

    note right of Idle: Other services can<br/>use freed VRAM
